title: Balinese Garden Stew
summary: Balinese Garden Stew might be just the main course you are searching for. Watching your figure? This gluten free and dairy free recipe has 409 calories, 22g of protein, and 20g of fat per serving. This recipe serves 1 and costs $2.83 per serving. A couple people made this recipe, and 21 would say it hit the spot. It can be enjoyed any time, but it is especially good for Autumn. Head to the store and pick up carrot, bok choy, sea salt, and a few other things to make it today. To use up the cashews you could follow this main course with the Baked Apples with Cranberries and Cashews as a dessert. With a spoonacular score of 94%, this dish is excellent. Try Garden Vegetable Stew, Meatball Garden Stew, and Balinese Grilled Chicken for similar recipes.
